high_descs: Turn around, walk to the sink, turn left, and face the table.
Walk around the table to the door, turn left, and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the plate in the fridge, close the fridge, open the fridge, get the plate, and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the table, turn right, and walk to the counter.
Open the cabinet under the counter, put the plate in the cabinet, and close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold plate in the cabinet below the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the left side of the wood table.
Pick up the grey plate on the wood table.
Turn left and walk around the table to the refrigerator.
Place the grey plate in the refrigerator to chill for a moment and then remove it.
Turn to your left and go to the cupboard directly underneath the sink on the right.
Open the cupboard and place the plate inside.
anns.task_desc: Chill the grey plate and place it in the cupboard underneath the sink.

high_descs: Turn around to face the sink, walk towards it, turn left at the sink, walk towards the wall, turn left to face the wooden table.
Pick up the grey plate from the wooden table.
Turn left, walk forward to turn right at the end of the table, then turn left and walk towards the fridge; stop in front of it.
Open both doors of the fridge, place the plate on the top right shelf, close the doors, then open the fridge doors and take the plate out of it, close the doors again.
Turn left, walk towards the sink, and stand in front of it.
Open the right cabinet underneath the sink, place the plate inside, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold plate underneath the sink.
